                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
                            <div contenteditable="false" style="height: 100%; width: 100%">
                                <div>
                                    <p>A code from the vocabulary shown indicating the function of the document author<br/>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>The  Coded Plain flavour of Coded Value (CV) datatype shall be used to carry this information  as follows:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>The <i>code</i> attribute shall contain the value                           </li>
                                    <li>The <i>codeSystem</i> attribute shall contain the OID for the vocabulary  concerned.                         </li>
