                        <text>This is a unique identifier for this instance of the observation.                                                                                                           <p> The Identifier Global datatype flavour is used to carry the first identifiers follows:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>The <em>root</em> attribute shall contain a DCE UUID.                                                                                                                                                </li>
